    </section>

    <!-- General Medicine Section -->
    <div class="container2">
        <div>
            <h1>BBMH Hospital – Best General Medicine Hospital in Bhilwara</h1>
            <img src="\images\GM.jpg" alt="General Medicine" class="img">
            <p>
                Looking for the best general medicine hospital in Bhilwara? Your search ends here. BBMH Hospital’s General Medicine Department is equipped with skilled physicians and advanced diagnostic facilities to ensure accurate assessment and effective treatment. We manage a wide range of acute and chronic illnesses, offering compassionate care to patients of all ages.
                Our internal medicine specialists focus on the prevention, diagnosis, and treatment of adult diseases. With a patient-centric approach, we aim to promote long-term wellness through early intervention and continuous medical support.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div>
            <h2>What Does General Medicine Cover?</h2>
            <ul class="ul">
                <li>Diagnosis and treatment of common ailments like fever, infections, and fatigue.</li>
                <li>Management of chronic diseases such as diabetes, hypertension, thyroid, and asthma.</li>
                <li>Preventive care including health screenings and lifestyle counseling.</li>
                <li>Coordination with specialists for complex or referred cases.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container3">
        <div class="wrapper" style="margin-top: 8vh;">
            <img src="\images\GM.webp" alt="General Physician Consultation">
            <div class="intro">
                <h2>Comprehensive Internal Medicine Services:</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Primary Care:</strong> Initial evaluation and long-term monitoring of health conditions.</li>
                    <li><strong>Chronic Disease Management:</strong> Specialized treatment plans for ongoing health issues.</li>
                    <li><strong>Diagnostic Expertise:</strong> Thorough analysis using pathology, imaging, and clinical tools.</li>
                    <li><strong>Preventive Health:</strong> Immunizations, check-ups, and lifestyle modifications.</li>
                    <li><strong>Emergency Care:</strong> Prompt treatment for acute symptoms and stabilization of patients.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr>

        <div class="wrapper1">
            <img src="\images\GM1.avif" alt="Infection Treatment">
            <div class="intro1">
                <h2>Infection Control & Treatment:</h2>
                <p>From seasonal viral infections to complex bacterial diseases, our team ensures accurate diagnosis and effective medication. Special focus is placed on patient isolation and hygiene during infectious outbreaks.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr>

        <div class="wrapper2">
            <img src="\images\GM2.jpg" alt="Lifestyle Disorder Management">
            <div class="intro2">
                <h2>Holistic Approach to Lifestyle Diseases:</h2>
                <p>Our specialists offer guidance and medical solutions for lifestyle disorders including obesity, hypertension, and insomnia. Stress and anxiety-related illnesses are also addressed through integrated care models.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr>

    <div class="video-container">
        <div style="padding: 2vh;">
            <h2>Why Choose BBMH Hospital for General Medicine in Bhilwara?</h2>
            <p>We bring a combination of clinical excellence, modern technology, and compassionate care to every patient. Here’s why our general medicine department stands out:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Experienced Physicians:</strong> Skilled in diagnosing complex and overlapping symptoms.</li>
                <li><strong>Modern Diagnostic Tools:</strong> Well-equipped labs and imaging units for accurate testing.</li>
                <li><strong>Personalized Care Plans:</strong> Tailored treatment strategies for every patient’s condition.</li>
                <li><strong>Emergency & ICU Access:</strong> Seamless transition to intensive care when required.</li>
                <li><strong>Continuity of Care:</strong> Regular follow-ups and coordination with specialists when needed.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>At BBMH Hospital in Bhilwara, we emphasize early diagnosis, evidence-based treatments, and preventive care to help you live a healthier life. Visit us for trusted and compassionate internal medicine services.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <!-- Toggle and Form Scripts -->
    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
            document.getElementById("toggleBtn").addEventListener("click", function () {
                let appointmentSection = document.getElementById("appointmentSection");
                appointmentSection.style.display = (appointmentSection.style.display === "none" || appointmentSection.style.display === "") ? "block" : "none";

                window.scrollTo({
                    top: 10,
                    behavior: "smooth"
                });
            });
        });
    </script>

    <!-- Bootstrap Validation -->
    <script>
        (() => {
            'use strict';
            const forms = document.querySelectorAll('.needs-validation');
            Array.from(forms).forEach(form => {
                form.addEventListener('submit', event => {
                    if (!form.checkValidity()) {
                        event.preventDefault();
                        event.stopPropagation();
                    }
                    form.classList.add('was-validated');
                }, false);
            });
        })();
    </script>

    <!-- External Libraries -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.5/gsap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.5/ScrollTrigger.min.js"></script>
    <script src="index.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
